Mozillz Taiwan (MozTW) 討論區提供使用 mozilla.org 產品的華人們交流與分享資訊，為了讓主機永保安康，請不要以程式 (bots) 到討論區上「砍站」(也就是 crawling, leeching...)，以免造成主機額外負擔。但個人「少量」擷取資料，只要不影響到主機穩定性不在此限。 

我們非常歡迎您參與社群，但也煩請考慮其他使用者，共體時艱。如果討論區 (或 Wiki) 無法正常運作，那對大家都沒有好處。我們正努力解決伺服器負擔問題，同時如果發現有「砍站」行為，不得已之下會封鎖該 IP。 

多謝您的配合，還請繼續支持 Mozilla Taiwan 各項服務。 

Mozillz Taiwan (MozTW) Forum is a support forum and an online community for all Chinese Mozilla.org products users. 

In order to keep the forum online, we would like to ask everybody not to download a copy of the forum database/content with scripts (or bots). In order words, do not crawl/leech MozTW Forum (or Wiki). Such behaviour is considered as selfish and is not acceptable in Mozilla Taiwan. But if you 

We welcome your participation, however, please be considerate of others. No one will be benefited if the Forum (or Wiki) is offline due to a few individuals' crawling. Any individual found crawling MozTW Forum and Wiki will be added to our blacklist (aka banned list).

Mozilla 正體中文/台灣
